You could filter pages in MedusWiki by describing its role and topic that it is associated with. There is ''Filter'' form in search window:

{data/images/filter1.png|filter form}
pic. 1

You could filter pages by role:

{data/images/filter2.png|filtering by role}
pic. 2 

You could filter pages by topic that it is associated with:

{data/images/filter3.png|filter form}
pic. 3 

You could filter pages by role and topic of the association: 

{data/images/filter4.png|filter form}
pic. 4 
